# baidu-ai-phpsdk
百度AI开放平台接口功能PHP SDK

## install
```bash
# 安装
composer require varmtone/baidu-ai-sdk
```

## example
```php
/**
 * 使用案例
 **/
use Bdai\AipSpeech;

//改成自己的配置
$appid = '00000000';
$appkey = '0000000000000000000000000000';
$secrectkey = '00000000000000000000000000000000000';

$speechAi = new AipSpeech($appid, $appkey, $secrectkey);

/**
 * 语音合成测试
 *
 **/
$res = $speechAi->tts('hello', 'zh', [
    'per'=>5
]);
echo base64_encode($res); //输出语音数据base64格式
echo "============================= \n";

/**
 * 语音识别测试
 */
//输入的语音数据
$audio = base64_decode('');
$res = $speechAi->asr($audio, 'pcm', []);
print_r($res);
```
也可以到demo目录执行下边命令
```php
cd demo
php index.php
```
